data.description: Welcome to this charming 1,300 square foot ranch home in sought-after Aragona Village, Virginia Beach! This meticulously maintained property was previously utilized as a successful short-term rental and is now available for you to make your own. Featuring an open floor plan, this home is in great condition and ready for immediate occupancy. The interior boasts ample natural light, making it feel warm and inviting. With three well-appointed bedrooms and two bathrooms, there's plenty of space for family and guests. One of the standout features of this property is the option for the furniture to convey, making your move-in process a breeze. This home is centrally located, providing easy access to nearby schools, shopping, and dining. Commuters will appreciate the convenience of being just moments away from I-264, making it a breeze to travel throughout Virginia Beach. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a turnkey property.
